cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.GR, cs.HC, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with image processing and object detection using depth information.
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper mentions the use of the detected hand positions to control robotic hands.
- cs.GR (Graphics) is a possibility as the paper deals with constructing virtual hands.
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is also possible as the paper discusses the use of hand gestures to interact with machines.
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is a less likely category but still possible as the paper deals with processing and analyzing multimedia data from the Kinect sensor.
